article_title: Patriots Notebook: Gostkowski's big moment has yet to kick in
article_text:
Patriots kicker Stephen Gostkowski lines up for a field goal, with holder Ryan Allen awaiting the snap, during the team's November game against the Lions. Gostkowski's true value may be put to the test in the playoffs. (USA TODAY Sports)

Patriots Notebook: Gostkowski's big moment has yet to kick in

article_metadata.description: THE distinction may not have been quite as prestigious as the first-team honors bestowed upon teammates Rob Gronkowski and Darrelle Revis, but Stephen Gostkowski's selection as a second-team All-Pro is just as deserved.
article_metadata.title: Patriots Notebook: Gostkowski's big moment has yet to kick in | New Hampshire
